OL,3,C#4bn electric car battery factory to
OL,4,Cbe built in Somerset
OL,6,FAround 4,000 jobs will be created for
OL,7,Fpeople to work in the multi-billion
OL,8,Fpound factory, which will be based at
OL,9,Fthe Gravity Smart Campus.
OL,11,FA spokesperson from battery
OL,12,Fmanufacturer Agratas, who has acquired
OL,13,Fthe factory, said: "It's hoped that by
OL,14,Fthe early 2030s, the facility will
OL,15,Fcontribute almost half of the
OL,16,Fprojected battery manufacturing
OL,17,Fcapacity required for the UK
OL,18,Fautomotive sector.
