OL,6,F"To realise the transformative
OL,7,Fpotential of the gigafactory, Agratas
OL,8,Fwill work closely with local and
OL,9,Fregional partners, including Somerset
OL,10,FCouncil, Bridgwater and Taunton
OL,11,FCollege, and the wider Gravity Smart
OL,12,FCampus, to deliver bespoke education
OL,13,Fand training programmes in the region,
OL,14,Fcreating local jobs for local people."
OL,16,FThousands of residents living near the
OL,17,Fsite of the future gigafactory campus
OL,18,Fare set to receive a leaflet through
OL,19,Fthe post this week, introducing
OL,20,FAgratas to the community.
