OL,8,Fpeople to follow Agratas' community
OL,9,FWhatsApp channel for regular updates
OL,10,Fon the site's progress.
OL,12,FTom Flack, CEO of Agratas, said: "Our
OL,13,Fmulti-billion-pound investment will
OL,14,Fbring state-of-the-art technology to
OL,15,FSomerset, helping to supercharge
OL,16,FBritain's transition to electric
OL,17,Fmobility whilst creating thousands of
OL,18,Fjobs in the process.
